message: Use the 'stove' tool on raw protein and vegetables to create valuable cooked items (value 20). Combining cooked protein with 1-2 cooked vegetables consistently yields high-value items (60-80). However, be cautious with grains; adding them to complex cooked dishes often creates 'overcomplicated' items with zero value.
